# 24 - Interview Prep Coach
# Prepare for job interviews

NAME interview-prep
INPUT role
INPUT company DEFAULT "tech company"
INPUT experience_level DEFAULT "mid-level"

GOAL research "Research typical $role interviews at a $company. Identify common question categories and expectations for $experience_level."
GOAL questions "Generate 15 likely questions across: technical, behavioral, situational, and role-specific."
GOAL frameworks "Provide answer frameworks: STAR method examples, technical explanation structures, and red flags to avoid."
GOAL practice "Create a mock interview script with questions, ideal answer points, and follow-up probes. Save the complete prep guide to interview-prep-output.md."

RUN prep USING research, questions, frameworks, practice
